name: Jinx (Teen Titans) LoRA
description:
Revised Dataset. Much more flexible than the previous version imo. Has trouble producing "slit pupils" or "snake eyes" so you'd have to inpaint those.

Recommended weight between 0.7-0.9; can go higher or lower depending on additional LoRAs, etc.

Generated Batch Size 6, and picked one seed. Then used Hi-Res Fix (Upscaler: 4x-UltraSharp) 2x —> Extras (Upscaler: 4x-UltraSharp) 2x

modelVersions.name: v1.5
trainedWords: Choker, light-violet collar, violet dress, striped leggings
modelVersions.description:
LoRA for Jinx from Teen Titans (2003). Trained v2.0 on AnythingV5, also 1st time using the network dim/alpha: 32/16 to produce a smaller file-size LoRA.

Backgrounds should be easier to detail now, and using additional art-sytles LoRAs seem to have improved (just need to lower this model's weight).

Recommended weight between 0.6-0.8; can go higher or lower depending on additional LoRAs, etc.

  • basic outfit: choker, light-violet collar, violet dress, striped leggings

  • extra: halloween bikni, braided pigtails

Used Hi-Res Fix (Latent) 2x —> Extras (4x-UltraSharp)
